parameters:
It seems that there are still those who refuse to give up and are
hiding. Leave the cleanup to us.
I surrender...! I'm just a small fry, so I don't know much.

Just... The innermost area where Mr. \n[21] and the former nobles come
and go should be locked. I don't know where it is either.

I heard that Megista was built on top of ruins from the Carbine
Dynasty era. It seems like they are also utilizing the pre-existing
underground ruins here.

So it's time to pay taxes... Well, I've had my fair share of good
food, so it's no big deal.
It seems like there's no one else here anymore...
There seems to be a boy who was brought here...

Cough, cough... I can't stop coughing since the black spots
appeared...

I did receive some medicine just in case, but it doesn't seem to be
working at all... I wonder if I'll be okay...
